{"tid":1661973,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"睇完中大聲明 不如睇埋樹仁email la","createTime":"2019-10-18T12:50:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-19T07:40:33.000Z","uid":274380,"like":52,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"f67885475c26c45200ba4fbfbcff496b9a61a9f9","tid":1661973,"uid":274380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T12:50:03.000Z","msg":"各位同學和老師：<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n香港正值非常時期，我們每天身處校園，目睹大家堅持追求知識、關心社會，委實令人安慰。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n同學置身當前大環境，面對著社會、家庭、朋友甚或日常生活的各種壓力，及不同程度的情緒困擾，如此種種情況，我們都明白理解。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n此時此刻，同學遇到學務與學則的問題，我們會基於合乎情理的原則，在現存的框架內，予以彈性處理。我們會考慮個別同學面對的具體困難，盡量給予其空間，讓同學的學習不受這些短期事件所困擾及影響。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n大學會繼續按既定課程大綱中的持續評估(Continuous Assessment)評核同學的學業進度。若同學因外界情況，而未能到校上課，例如：公共交通停駛或在上學途中遇到突發情況等等，本學期內一律不視作缺席論。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n各學系老師的授課，在許可的情況下，課堂教學錄影將會繼續上載到內聯網(Moodle)內，以輔助大家學習。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n若有同學因事遭受到法律控訴，根據香港實行的普通法奉行無罪推定的原則，即在法庭裁定前均假定無罪，學校亦會尊重法治精神，按此原則處理相關學則事宜。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n在現行學則下，學生因特別事故需要休學，可向助理副校長(註冊處)提出申請，助理副校長會對有關申請作出通盤考慮。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n育德立仁是創辦樹仁大學的初心，我們時刻在念。各位同學如有情緒、學習或其他方面問題，請撥熱線：2570-7110，聯絡我們。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n胡懷中<br />\n<br />\n二零一九年十月十八日<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>睇完有咩感想</strong></span>"},{"pid":"a383553797b65abf9cb96134a1c79aa39e4f2393","tid":1661973,"uid":299360,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T12:51:52.000Z","msg":"一大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：八大人 非tree u 純佩服"},{"pid":"a707695b06e9db9fc5002491af7ef81dd15dff03","tid":1661973,"uid":217844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T12:52:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好好"},{"pid":"6bc39ad7befb7ad228675c911ee2c1acc15cc2b9","tid":1661973,"uid":78060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T12:55:05.000Z","msg":"一大<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ea299a8b7e42b7238573a010c3b7c2948b1f916","tid":1661973,"uid":325059,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T13:00:45.000Z","msg":"字裏行間充滿人情味"},{"pid":"6bee09cdc1d53a9103a16fec239e2ff4e1899b4c","tid":1661973,"uid":89336,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T13:09:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一大！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3293b9994c5b1903c582812091f3155cc6b58110","tid":1661973,"uid":145277,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T13:25:34.000Z","msg":"樹仁個春袋唔喺政府度，自然講嘢可以大聲D。<br />\n<br />\n不過我個人欣賞段王爺多d，唔怕俾人炒"},{"pid":"0b45d7c1b2856452fe0ee49a21a35f2b87097570","tid":1661973,"uid":95181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T13:55:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e452848681caccfca53890c59cf447f487d93af","tid":1661973,"uid":2607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T13:56:15.000Z","msg":"屈"},{"pid":"26980e191a08c2983df25642a1a9ade969eaa778","tid":1661973,"uid":87305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T13:57:37.000Z","msg":"樹人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b5f285efc0d4431961668afcc43a2c401fe1c26","tid":1661973,"uid":179422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T13:57:56.000Z","msg":"母校我驕傲🤘🏼🤘🏼"},{"pid":"e2313fcf6453233934dff425b6ba30448d70e40b","tid":1661973,"uid":61106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T14:03:44.000Z","msg":"其實佢無講啲咩炸wor, 有事番唔到唔當abs係基本要有，其他字句都無指責警方，陣係話無罪推